## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **nintedanib Ofev SSc-ILD 2019** = first FDA SSc-ILD (2014 IPF 후 5년). SENSCIS trial 52주 FVC 감소 둔화. multi-kinase (TGF-β + VEGFR + PDGFR + FGFR). quantum-VQE 의 multi-kinase selectivity 가 fit.
2. **tocilizumab Actemra SSc-ILD 2021** = first FDA SSc-ILD progression. focuSSced trial 48주 FVC 보존. IL-6R 차단이 fibrosis 진행 둔화. quantum-VQE 의 IL-6R Fab geometry leverage.
3. **pirfenidone Esbriet 2014 IPF** = SSc-ILD off-label. multi-target anti-fibrotic (TGF-β + TNF-α + ROS). 작용 mechanism 한정 — quantum-VQE fit 약함.
4. **mycophenolate + cyclophosphamide IV pulse** = 만성 SSc-ILD 1L 표준. SLS-II trial mycophenolate ≈ cyclophosphamide 비열등. 만성 IMPDH + alkylator 표준.
5. **rituximab + abatacept Phase 2/3** = 만성 SSc 진행 — 임상 의미 한정. anti-CD20 + CTLA4-Ig mechanism fit 가 약하지만 quantum-VQE Fab geometry 재활용 가능.
6. **HSCT autologous severe SSc** = ASTIS/SCOT trials — refractory severe dcSSc 의 OS + EFS 향상. cyclophosphamide pre-conditioning + ATG. cross-bone_marrow_failure + transplant.
7. **ACE-i 만성 SSc 신장 위기 응급 1L** = captopril + lisinopril. corticosteroid > 15mg avoid (renal crisis 위험 — controversial). 만성 SSc 응급 standard of care.
8. **bosentan + macitentan + ambrisentan + prostacyclin (epoprostenol/treprostinil/iloprost) + selexipag + sildenafil/tadalafil + riociguat + sotatercept 2024** = 만성 SSc-PAH multi-pathway. ETA + IP + PDE5 + sGC + ActR2 5-pathway. cross-pulmonology PAH.
9. **simtuzumab + ziritaxestat failure** = LOXL2 + LPA1 mechanism Phase 2/3 failure. fibrosis target validation 한정 — quantum-VQE 의 post-mortem 가치.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, SSc 임상 의미 한정.

